spec_data.Name: bind-pkcs11-utils
spec_data.Description:
This is a set of PKCS#11 utilities that when used together create rsa
keys in a PKCS11 keystore. Also utilities for working with DNSSEC
compiled with native PKCS#11 functionality are included.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Mon 13 Nov 2017 02:34:08 PM EST, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Bind tools with native PKCS#11 for using DNSSEC
